📝 Instructions for Nourhan & Mahmoud Omer:

You need to complete both functions:

Function 1: _draw_button_image()

    Creates a visual button image with text centered on it
    Returns a PhotoImage that can be displayed in Tkinter

Function 2: _update_button_text()

    Updates an existing button with new text
    Redraws the button while keeping the same colors
    Prevents image garbage collection

These functions work together to create and update interactive buttons! 🎨
